### ðŸ”– **Pro Tip for Interview:**

```java
Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> {
    for(int i = 0; i < 5; i++) System.out.println("Lambda Hi");
});
t1.start();
```

> âœ… Lambda can be used with functional interfaces like `Runnable`.

